      <title>Hugo Features Demo: Images, Code, Math &amp; More</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/hugo-features-demo-images-code-math-more/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Aug 2025 12:15:44 +0800</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/hugo-features-demo-images-code-math-more/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;hugo-features-demo-images-code-math--more&#34;&gt;Hugo Features Demo: Images, Code, Math &amp;amp; More&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;This post demonstrates various features available in Hugo blog posts, including images, code blocks, math formulas, and media embeds.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;1-inserting-local-images&#34;&gt;1. Inserting Local Images&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;To add local images to your blog posts:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;step-1-create-the-image-directory&#34;&gt;Step 1: Create the image directory&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;background-color:#f0f0f0;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;mkdir -p static/images&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id=&#34;step-2-add-your-image-file&#34;&gt;Step 2: Add your image file&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Place your image in &lt;code&gt;/static/images/your-image.jpg&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;step-3-reference-in-markdown&#34;&gt;Step 3: Reference in markdown&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;background-color:#f0f0f0;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-markdown&#34; data-lang=&#34;markdown&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;![&lt;span style=&#34;color:#062873;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;Alt text for the image&lt;/span&gt;](&lt;span style=&#34;color:#4070a0&#34;&gt;/images/your-image.jpg&lt;/span&gt;)&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Example with actual image:&lt;/strong&gt;&#xA;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/images/openai-logo.png&#34; alt=&#34;OpenAI Logo&#34; title=&#34;OpenAI Logo&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
